<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SpendSense AI — Understand your spending</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.0/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<style>
  :root{
    --navy-950:#05070d;
    --navy-900:#0a0e1a;
    --navy-800:#11162a;
    --navy-700:#1a2138;
    --line:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    --line-strong:rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
    --ink:#f5f7fb;
    --ink-dim:#9aa5c0;
    --ink-faint:#5c6684;
    --pulse:#34e8b0;
    --pulse-dim:#1c8f6d;
    --pulse-soft:rgba(52,232,176,0.12);
    --amber:#f6b94a;
    --coral:#ff7069;
    --indigo:#7c8cf8;
    --radius-sm:10px;
    --radius:16px;
    --radius-lg:22px;
    --radius-xl:28px;
    --shadow-sm:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    --shadow-md:0 8px 24px -8px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
    --shadow-lg:0 24px 60px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    --shadow-glow: 0 8px 28px -6px rgba(52,232,176,0.35);
    --ease: cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
    --display: 'Manrope', 'Inter', sans-serif;
    --body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    --mono: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  }

  html[data-theme="light"]{
    --navy-950:#f4f6fb;
    --navy-900:#e9edf5;
    --navy-800:#ffffff;
    --navy-700:#eef1f8;
    --line:rgba(15,23,42,0.08);
    --line-strong:rgba(15,23,42,0.15);
    --ink:#10141f;
    --ink-dim:#525c78;
    --ink-faint:#818aa3;
    --pulse:#0fae7c;
    --pulse-dim:#0c8a63;
    --pulse-soft:rgba(15,174,124,0.1);
    --amber:#b8770f;
    --coral:#d9433c;
    --indigo:#4d54d6;
    --shadow-sm:0 1px 2px rgba(15,23,42,0.06);
    --shadow-md:0 8px 24px -8px rgba(15,23,42,0.12), 0 2px 6px rgba(15,23,42,0.07);
    --shadow-lg:0 24px 60px -20px rgba(15,23,42,0.16), 0 4px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);
    --shadow-glow: 0 8px 24px -6px rgba(15,174,124,0.28);
  }
  html[data-theme="light"] body{
    background:
      radial-gradient(1100px 520px at 12% -8%, rgba(15,174,124,0.05), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(900px 480px at 88% 0%, rgba(77,84,214,0.045), transparent 55%),
      var(--navy-950);
  }
  html[data-theme="light"] .hero .accent{
    background:linear-gradient(120deg, var(--pulse), #0c8a63 60%, var(--pulse));
    -webkit-background-clip:text; background-clip:text; color:transparent;
  }
  html[data-theme="light"] .nav{ background:rgba(244,246,251,0.78); }
  html[data-theme="light"] .avatar{ color:var(--pulse-dim); }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;}
  html,body{margin:0;padding:0;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    background:
      radial-gradient(1100px 520px at 12% -8%, rgba(52,232,176,0.07), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(900px 480px at 88% 0%, rgba(124,140,248,0.06), transparent 55%),
      var(--navy-950);
    color:var(--ink);
    font-family:var(--body);
    line-height:1.55;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
    -moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;
  }

  h1,h2,h3,h4{font-family:var(--display); margin:0; letter-spacing:-0.02em; font-weight:700;}
  p{margin:0;}
  a{color:inherit;}
  button{font-family:var(--body); cursor:pointer; transition:.18s var(--ease);}
  button:focus-visible, input:focus-visible, select:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--pulse); outline-offset:2px;}
  ::selection{background:var(--pulse); color:var(--navy-950);}
  ::-webkit-scrollbar{width:10px; height:10px;}
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:transparent;}
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--line-strong); border-radius:99px;}

  @keyframes fadeInUp{
    from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(10px);}
    to{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn{ from{opacity:0;} to{opacity:1;} }
  @keyframes pulseGlow{
    0%,100%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(62,242,197,0.35);}
    50%{box-shadow:0 0 0 6px rgba(62,242,197,0);}
  }

  .screen{display:none; min-height:100vh;}
  .screen.active{display:block; animation:fadeIn .35s var(--ease);}

  /* ---------- NAV ---------- */
  .nav{
    position:sticky; top:0; z-index:50;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    padding:16px 32px;
    background:rgba(5,7,13,0.72);
    backdrop-filter:blur(16px) saturate(160%);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(16px) saturate(160%);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .nav-logo{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; font-family:var(--display); font-weight:800; font-size:18px; letter-spacing:-0.01em;}
  .nav-logo .dot-pulse{
    width:11px;height:11px;border-radius:50%;
    background:radial-gradient(circle at 32% 30%, #baffe6, var(--pulse) 60%, var(--pulse-dim));
    box-shadow:0 0 0 4px var(--pulse-soft), 0 0 14px rgba(62,242,197,0.55);
    animation:pulseGlow 2.6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .nav-links{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:2px;}
  .nav-links button{font-size:13.5px;}
  .navbtn{
    background:transparent; border:1px solid transparent; color:var(--ink-dim);
    padding:9px 16px; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); font-weight:600; transition:.18s var(--ease);
    position:relative;
  }
  .navbtn::after{
    content:''; position:absolute; left:16px; right:16px; bottom:3px; height:1.5px;
    background:var(--pulse); transform:scaleX(0); transform-origin:left; transition:transform .25s var(--ease);
  }
  .navbtn:hover::after{transform:scaleX(1);}
  .navbtn.primary::after{display:none;}
  .navbtn:hover{color:var(--ink); border-color:var(--line-strong); background:rgba(255,255,255,0.045); backdrop-filter:blur(10px);}
  .navbtn.primary{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pulse), var(--pulse-dim)); color:var(--navy-950);
    font-weight:700; box-shadow:var(--shadow-glow); border-radius:999px; padding:9px 20px;
  }
  .navbtn.primary:hover{background:linear-gradient(135deg, #7ef8d9, var(--pulse)); transform:translateY(-1px); box-shadow:0 12px 34px -6px rgba(62,242,197,0.5);}
  .nav-user{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; font-size:13.5px; color:var(--ink-dim); font-weight:500;}
  .theme-toggle{
    width:36px; height:36px; border-radius:50%; border:1px solid var(--line-strong);
    background:var(--navy-800); color:var(--ink-dim); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    transition:.2s var(--ease); flex-shrink:0;
  }
  .theme-toggle:hover{color:var(--ink); border-color:var(--pulse-dim); transform:translateY(-1px);}
  .theme-toggle svg{width:16px; height:16px;}
  .theme-toggle .theme-icon-moon{display:none;}
  html[data-theme="light"] .theme-toggle .theme-icon-sun{display:none;}
  html[data-theme="light"] .theme-toggle .theme-icon-moon{display:block;}
  .avatar{
    width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%; background:linear-gradient(155deg, var(--navy-700), var(--navy-800));
    border:1px solid var(--line-strong); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; color:var(--pulse); font-weight:600;
  }

  .wrap{max-width:1120px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 32px;}

  /* ---------- LANDING ---------- */
  .hero{
    padding:110px 32px 88px; text-align:center; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  }
  .hero-pulse{max-width:760px; margin:0 auto 40px; height:90px; filter:drop-shadow(0 8px 24px rgba(52,232,176,0.25));}
  .hero h1{font-size:clamp(40px,6vw,74px); font-weight:800; line-height:1.04; letter-spacing:-0.03em;}
  .hero .accent{
    background:linear-gradient(120deg, var(--pulse), #7ff5d4 60%, var(--pulse));
    -webkit-background-clip:text; background-clip:text; color:transparent;
  }
  .hero p.sub{max-width:560px; margin:24px auto 0; color:var(--ink-dim); font-size:18px; line-height:1.6;}
  .cta-row{display:flex; gap:14px; justify-content:center; margin-top:40px; flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .hero-mockup{
    max-width:920px; margin:56px auto 0; border-radius:var(--radius-lg); overflow:hidden;
    border:1px solid var(--line-strong); box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg); background:var(--navy-800);
    animation:fadeInUp .5s var(--ease);
  }
  .hero-mockup-bar{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; padding:10px 14px; background:var(--navy-900); border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
  .hero-mockup-bar span{width:9px; height:9px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--line-strong); display:inline-block;}
  .hero-mockup img{display:block; width:100%; height:auto;}
  .card-icon{
    width:42px; height:42px; border-radius:12px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    margin-bottom:14px; background:var(--pulse-soft); color:var(--pulse);
  }
  .card-icon svg{width:21px; height:21px;}
  .btn{
    padding:14px 26px; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); border:1px solid var(--line-strong);
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.035); backdrop-filter:blur(14px); -webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
    color:var(--ink); font-weight:600; font-size:14.5px; transition:.2s var(--ease);
  }
  .btn.primary{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pulse), var(--pulse-dim));
    color:var(--navy-950); border-color:transparent; box-shadow:var(--shadow-glow);
  }
  .btn.primary:hover{background:linear-gradient(135deg, #7ef8d9, var(--pulse)); transform:translateY(-2px); box-shadow:0 16px 40px -8px rgba(62,242,197,0.55);}
  .btn:hover{border-color:var(--pulse-dim); transform:translateY(-2px); background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07); box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);}
  .btn:active{transform:translateY(0); transition-duration:.05s;}

  .section{padding:80px 32px; border-top:1px solid var(--line);}
  .section .eyebrow{color:var(--pulse); font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12.5px; letter-spacing:.1em; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:600;}
  .section h2{font-size:clamp(26px,3.2vw,34px); margin-top:12px; max-width:620px; line-height:1.25;}
  .grid3{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:20px; margin-top:44px;}
  .grid2{display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.1fr 0.9fr; gap:52px; align-items:center; margin-top:44px;}
  @media(max-width:860px){.grid3{grid-template-columns:1fr;} .grid2{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
  .card{
    background:linear-gradient(160deg, var(--navy-800), var(--navy-900));
   
    border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); padding:28px;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); transition:.25s var(--ease);
  }
  .card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px); border-color:var(--line-strong); box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);}
  .card h3{font-size:17px; margin-bottom:9px; font-weight:700;}
  .card p{color:var(--ink-dim); font-size:14px; line-height:1.6;}
  .num-tag{font-family:var(--mono); color:var(--pulse-dim); font-size:12.5px; margin-bottom:16px; display:block; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.03em;}

  .footer-cta{text-align:center; padding:100px 32px; border-top:1px solid var(--line);}
  .footer-cta h2{font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,38px); margin-bottom:24px;}
  .foot{padding:32px 32px; text-align:center; color:var(--ink-faint); font-size:12.5px; border-top:1px solid var(--line);}

  /* ---------- AUTH ---------- */
  .auth-shell{
    min-height:100vh; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:32px;
    background:radial-gradient(700px 420px at 50% 0%, rgba(62,242,197,0.06), transparent 60%);
  }
  .auth-card{
    width:100%; max-width:420px; background:linear-gradient(165deg, var(--navy-800), var(--navy-900));
    border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:var(--radius-xl); padding:42px;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg); animation:fadeInUp .4s var(--ease);
  }
  .auth-card h2{font-size:26px; margin-bottom:7px; font-weight:800;}
  .auth-card p.hint{color:var(--ink-dim); font-size:14px; margin-bottom:30px; line-height:1.55;}
  .field{margin-bottom:16px;}
  .field label{display:block; font-size:12.5px; color:var(--ink-dim); margin-bottom:7px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.01em;}
  .field input, .field select{
    width:100%; padding:12px 14px; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); border:1px solid var(--line-strong);
    background:var(--navy-900); color:var(--ink); font-size:14px; font-family:var(--body); transition:.18s var(--ease);
  }
  .field input:focus, .field select:focus, .field textarea:focus{
    outline:none; border-color:var(--pulse-dim); box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--pulse-soft);
  }
  .auth-submit{
    width:100%; margin-top:10px; padding:14px; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); border:none;
    background:var(--pulse); color:var(--navy-950); font-weight:700; font-size:15px;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow-glow); transition:.2s var(--ease);
  }
  .auth-submit:hover{background:#7ef8d9; transform:translateY(-1px); box-shadow:0 12px 32px -6px rgba(62,242,197,0.45);}
  .auth-switch{margin-top:22px; text-align:center; font-size:13.5px; color:var(--ink-dim);}
  .auth-switch button{background:none; border:none; color:var(--pulse); font-weight:600; padding:0;}
  .auth-switch button:hover{color:#7ef8d9;}
  .auth-error{background:rgba(255,112,105,0.1); border:1px solid rgba(255,112,105,0.4); color:#ffb3ae; padding:11px 14px; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); font-size:13px; margin-bottom:16px; display:none;}

  /* ---------- APP SHELL ---------- */
  .app-body{padding:36px 32px 90px;}
  .app-head{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-end; margin-bottom:30px; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:16px;}
  .app-head h1{font-size:27px; letter-spacing:-0.02em;}
  .app-head p{color:var(--ink-dim); font-size:14px; margin-top:5px;}
  .tab-row{
    display:flex; gap:4px; margin-bottom:32px; flex-wrap:wrap;
    background:var(--navy-800); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:14px; padding:5px;
  }
  .tab{
    padding:9px 16px; border-radius:10px; border:1px solid transparent; background:transparent;
    color:var(--ink-dim); font-size:13.5px; font-weight:600; transition:.18s var(--ease);
  }
  .tab:hover{color:var(--ink);}
  .tab.active{background:var(--navy-950); color:var(--pulse); box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm), inset 0 0 0 1px var(--line-strong);}

  .stat-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:16px; margin-bottom:24px;}
  @media(max-width:900px){.stat-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}}
  .stat-card{
    background:linear-gradient(160deg, var(--navy-800), var(--navy-900)); border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:var(--radius); padding:20px; transition:.2s var(--ease);
  }
  .stat-card:hover{border-color:var(--line-strong); transform:translateY(-2px);}
  .stat-card .label{color:var(--ink-faint); font-size:11.5px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.07em; font-family:var(--mono); font-weight:500;}
  .stat-card .value{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:25px; margin-top:9px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-0.01em;}
  .stat-card .value.green{color:var(--pulse);}
  .stat-card .value.amber{color:var(--amber);}
  .stat-card .value.coral{color:var(--coral);}

  .panel-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.3fr 1fr; gap:20px;}
  @media(max-width:900px){.panel-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
  .panel{
    background:linear-gradient(160deg, var(--navy-800), var(--navy-900)); border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:var(--radius-lg); padding:26px; box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  .panel:hover{border-color:var(--line-strong); box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);}
  .panel h3{font-size:15.5px; margin-bottom:18px; font-weight:700;}
  .empty-state{text-align:center; padding:44px 20px; color:var(--ink-dim);}
  .empty-state .btn{margin-top:18px;}

  .risk-badge{display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; padding:7px 15px; border-radius:999px; font-size:12.5px; font-weight:700; font-family:var(--mono); letter-spacing:.02em;}
  .risk-badge.low{background:rgba(62,242,197,0.13); color:var(--pulse); box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(62,242,197,0.25);}
  .risk-badge.balanced{background:rgba(246,185,74,0.13); color:var(--amber); box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(246,185,74,0.25);}
  .risk-badge.high{background:rgba(255,112,105,0.13); color:var(--coral); box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,112,105,0.25);}
  .risk-badge .dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:currentColor;}

  /* ---------- FORM ---------- */
  .form-shell{max-width:760px; margin:0 auto;}
  .form-section{margin-bottom:30px;}
  .form-section h4{font-size:13px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.07em; color:var(--ink-faint); font-family:var(--mono); margin-bottom:15px; font-weight:600;}
  .savings-preview{background:var(--navy-900); border:1px solid var(--line-strong); border-radius:var(--radius); padding:18px 20px;}
  .savings-preview-row{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; font-family:var(--mono); font-size:14px; color:var(--ink-dim); padding:6px 0;}
  .savings-preview-total{border-top:1px solid var(--line); margin-top:6px; padding-top:12px; font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:var(--pulse);}
  .savings-preview-total.deficit{color:var(--coral);}
  .savings-preview-hint{color:var(--ink-faint); font-size:12px; margin-top:12px; line-height:1.55;}
  .cat-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); gap:14px;}
  @media(max-width:640px){.cat-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
  .cat-field{
    background:var(--navy-800); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:var(--radius); padding:15px 17px;
    transition:.2s var(--ease);
  }
  .cat-field:focus-within{border-color:var(--pulse-dim); box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--pulse-soft);}
  .cat-field label{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; font-size:13px; color:var(--ink-dim); margin-bottom:9px; font-weight:500;}
  .cat-field input{width:100%; background:transparent; border:none; color:var(--ink); font-family:var(--mono); font-size:20px; padding:0; font-weight:600;}
  .cat-field input:focus{outline:none;}
  .cat-icon{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%; box-shadow:0 0 6px currentColor;}

  /* ---------- RESULTS ---------- */
  .result-hero{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-800), var(--navy-900));
    border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:var(--radius-xl); padding:38px; margin-bottom:24px;
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:20px;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow-md); position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  }
  .result-hero::before{
    content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; pointer-events:none;
    background:radial-gradient(420px 220px at 100% 0%, rgba(62,242,197,0.08), transparent 70%);
  }
  .result-hero .waveform{width:220px; height:60px; position:relative;}
  .insight-list, .rec-list{list-style:none; margin:0; padding:0;}
  .insight-list li, .rec-list li{
    padding:15px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); display:flex; gap:12px; font-size:14px; color:var(--ink-dim); line-height:1.55;
  }
  .insight-list li:last-child, .rec-list li:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
  .insight-list li::before{content:"◆"; color:var(--pulse); font-size:9px; margin-top:5px;}
  .rec-list li{counter-increment:rec;}
  .rec-list{counter-reset:rec;}
  .rec-list li::before{content:counter(rec); font-family:var(--mono); color:var(--navy-950); background:var(--pulse); width:21px; height:21px; border-radius:50%; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:11px; flex-shrink:0; font-weight:700; box-shadow:var(--shadow-glow);}

  /* ---------- CHATBOT ---------- */
  .chat-shell{max-width:680px; margin:0 auto; background:linear-gradient(160deg, var(--navy-800), var(--navy-900)); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:var(--radius-xl); display:flex; flex-direction:column; box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);}
  .chat-answer{padding:30px 26px; min-height:180px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center;}
  .chat-answer-placeholder{color:var(--ink-faint); font-size:14px; text-align:center;}
  .chat-answer-q{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:11px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.07em; color:var(--pulse); margin-bottom:11px; font-weight:600;}
  .chat-answer-text{font-size:15px; line-height:1.75; color:var(--ink); animation:fadeIn .3s var(--ease);}
  .chat-suggest{display:flex; gap:8px; padding:0 26px 16px; flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .chip{background:var(--navy-900); border:1px solid var(--line-strong); color:var(--ink-dim); font-size:12px; padding:7px 13px; border-radius:999px; font-weight:500; transition:.18s var(--ease);}
  .chip:hover{border-color:var(--pulse-dim); color:var(--ink); background:var(--navy-700); transform:translateY(-1px);}
  .chat-input-row{display:flex; gap:10px; padding:18px; border-top:1px solid var(--line);}
  .chat-input-row input{flex:1; background:var(--navy-900); border:1px solid var(--line-strong); border-radius:var(--radius-sm); padding:12px 15px; color:var(--ink); font-size:14px; transition:.18s var(--ease);}
  .chat-input-row input:focus{outline:none; border-color:var(--pulse-dim); box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--pulse-soft);}
  .chat-input-row button{background:var(--pulse); border:none; color:var(--navy-950); border-radius:var(--radius-sm); padding:0 22px; font-weight:700; box-shadow:var(--shadow-glow);}
  .chat-input-row button:hover{background:#7ef8d9; transform:translateY(-1px);}

  /* ---------- PROGRESS ---------- */
  .history-row{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; padding:16px 4px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); font-size:14px; transition:.15s var(--ease); border-radius:10px;}
  .history-row:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);}

  /* ---------- ADVICE ---------- */
  .adv-item{padding:19px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
  .adv-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
  .adv-item-head{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:baseline; margin-bottom:9px; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:6px;}
  .adv-item-head h4{font-size:15px; font-family:var(--body); font-weight:700;}
  .adv-item-amounts{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:13px; color:var(--ink-faint);}
  .adv-bar-track{height:8px; border-radius:99px; background:var(--navy-900); overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:11px; border:1px solid var(--line);}
  .adv-bar-fill{height:100%; border-radius:99px; background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--pulse-dim), var(--pulse)); transition:width .5s var(--ease);}
  .adv-bar-fill.over{background:linear-gradient(90deg, #b8443f, var(--coral));}
  .adv-item p{color:var(--ink-dim); font-size:13.5px; line-height:1.6;}
  .week-card{background:var(--navy-900); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:var(--radius); padding:17px; transition:.2s var(--ease);}
  .week-card:hover{border-color:var(--line-strong);}
  .week-card h4{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:11.5px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.07em; color:var(--pulse); margin-bottom:11px; font-weight:600;}
  .week-card ul{margin:0; padding-left:18px; color:var(--ink-dim); font-size:13.5px; line-height:1.9;}

  /* ---------- MINI CALCULATOR (side-by-side sidebar) ---------- */
  .form-with-calc{display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 300px; gap:28px; align-items:start;}
  @media(max-width:900px){ .form-with-calc{grid-template-columns:1fr;} }
  .calc-sidebar{
    background:linear-gradient(160deg, var(--navy-800), var(--navy-900)); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); padding:22px;
    position:sticky; top:88px; box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  .calc-sidebar-head{font-weight:700; font-size:15px; margin-bottom:7px; font-family:var(--display);}
  .calc-sidebar-hint{color:var(--ink-dim); font-size:12.5px; margin-bottom:16px; line-height:1.5;}
  .calc-display{
    background:var(--navy-950); border:1px solid var(--line-strong); border-radius:var(--radius-sm);
    padding:15px 13px; text-align:right; font-family:var(--mono); font-size:24px; font-weight:500;
    margin-bottom:12px; overflow-x:auto; white-space:nowrap;
  }
  .calc-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4, 1fr); gap:8px; margin-bottom:16px;}
  .calc-btn{
    background:var(--navy-900); border:1px solid var(--line); color:var(--ink);
    border-radius:var(--radius-sm); padding:13px 0; font-size:15px; font-family:var(--mono); font-weight:500;
    transition:.12s var(--ease);
  }
  .calc-btn:hover{border-color:var(--pulse-dim); background:var(--navy-700);}
  .calc-btn:active{transform:scale(.94);}
  .calc-btn-op{color:var(--pulse);}
  .calc-btn-wide{grid-column:span 2;}
  .calc-btn-equals{background:var(--pulse); color:var(--navy-950); border-color:var(--pulse); font-weight:700; box-shadow:var(--shadow-glow);}
  .calc-btn-equals:hover{background:#7ef8d9;}
  .calc-tally{border-top:1px solid var(--line); padding-top:14px;}
  .calc-tally-head{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; font-size:11.5px; color:var(--ink-faint); font-family:var(--mono); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.06em; margin-bottom:9px; font-weight:500;}
  .calc-tally-head button{background:none; border:none; color:var(--ink-faint); font-size:11px; text-decoration:underline; padding:0;}
  .calc-tally-head button:hover{color:var(--coral);}
  .calc-tally-list{max-height:120px; overflow-y:auto; margin-bottom:9px;}
  .calc-tally-item{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; font-family:var(--mono); font-size:13px; color:var(--ink-dim); padding:6px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
  .calc-tally-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
  .calc-tally-item button{background:none; border:none; color:var(--ink-faint); font-size:13px; padding:0 4px;}
  .calc-tally-item button:hover{color:var(--coral);}
  .calc-tally-total{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:var(--pulse); text-align:right; margin-top:5px;}

  .history-row:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
  .history-row .date{color:var(--ink-faint); font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px;}

  canvas{max-width:100%;}
  .tab-icon{display:inline-flex; margin-right:7px; vertical-align:-3px;}
  .tab-icon svg{width:15px; height:15px;}
  .sr-only{position:absolute; width:1px;height:1px; overflow:hidden; clip:rect(0,0,0,0);}
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){ *{animation:none !important; transition:none !important;} }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ============ LANDING ============ -->
<div class="screen active" id="screen-landing">
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="nav-logo"><span class="dot-pulse"></span>SpendSense AI</div>
    <div class="nav-links" id="landing-nav-links">
      <button class="theme-toggle" onclick="toggleTheme()" title="Toggle light/dark mode" aria-label="Toggle light and dark mode">
        <svg class="theme-icon-sun" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/><path d="M12 2v2M12 20v2M4.9 4.9l1.4 1.4M17.7 17.7l1.4 1.4M2 12h2M20 12h2M4.9 19.1l1.4-1.4M17.7 6.3l1.4-1.4"/></svg>
        <svg class="theme-icon-moon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12.5A8.5 8.5 0 1 1 11.5 3a6.5 6.5 0 0 0 9.5 9.5z"/></svg>
      </button>
      <button class="navbtn" onclick="go('admin-login')" style="opacity:.6; font-size:12px;">Quick access</button>
      <button class="navbtn" onclick="go('login')">Log in</button>
      <button class="navbtn primary" onclick="go('signup')">Sign up</button>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <svg class="hero-pulse" viewBox="0 0 760 90" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <polyline points="0,45 90,45 115,15 140,75 165,45 300,45 320,25 340,65 360,45 500,45 525,10 550,80 575,45 760,45"
        stroke="#2fe6ad" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none" opacity="0.9"/>
    </svg>
    <h1>Understand your <span class="accent">spending</span>.<br>Build smarter money habits.</h1>
    <p class="sub">SpendSense AI reads your spending like a pulse — steady, balanced, or racing — and turns it into plain-language guidance built for teens.</p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <button class="btn primary" onclick="go('signup')">Start Your Spending Analysis</button>
      <button class="btn" onclick="go('login')">I already have an account</button>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-mockup">
      <div class="hero-mockup-bar"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="SpendSense AI dashboard showing income, spending, savings, and behaviour risk">
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
    <h2>What is SpendSense AI?</h2>
    <div class="grid2">
      <div>
        <p style="color:var(--ink-dim); font-size:16px; line-height:1.7;">
          SpendSense AI is an AI-powered financial behaviour assistant built specifically for teenagers.
          Enter your income and spending across eight everyday categories, and it turns those numbers into
          a clear, plain-language read on your habits — a risk category, personalized insights, a 4-week
          improvement plan, and a chatbot you can ask anything about your money.
        </p>
        <p style="color:var(--ink-dim); font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; margin-top:16px;">
          Every recommendation is grounded in real data: your own numbers, compared against a benchmark of
          real student spending and a much larger sample of real financial records — not guesswork or
          generic advice.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="num-tag">// the idea</span>
        <h3>Built for teens, not repurposed banking software</h3>
        <p>Most budgeting tools are built for adults with mortgages and paychecks. SpendSense AI starts from allowance-and-part-time-job money instead, and speaks in plain language rather than financial jargon.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid3">
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="8" ry="3"/><path d="M4 5v14c0 1.7 3.6 3 8 3s8-1.3 8-3V5"/><path d="M4 12c0 1.7 3.6 3 8 3s8-1.3 8-3"/></svg></div><span class="num-tag">01</span><h3>Real data, not guesses</h3><p>Every comparison and reference number comes from real datasets — thousands of real spending and financial records, not invented averages.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 11.5a8.4 8.4 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.4 8.4 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.4 8.4 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.4 8.4 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"/><path d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01"/></svg></div><span class="num-tag">02</span><h3>AI that explains itself</h3><p>Instead of just a score, you get the reasoning behind it — which categories are driving your result and specifically what to try next.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4" y="11" width="16" height="9" rx="1.5"/><path d="M8 11V7a4 4 0 0 1 7.5-2"/></svg></div><span class="num-tag">03</span><h3>Free to use, always available</h3><p>No sign-up fees, no paywalled insights. Run an analysis, ask the assistant a question, and get a real answer any time.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <span class="eyebrow">The problem</span>
    <h2>Most teens have never seen their own spending pattern — just their bank balance.</h2>
    <div class="grid3">
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M1 12s4-7 11-7 11 7 11 7-4 7-11 7-11-7-11-7z" stroke-dasharray="2 3"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg></div><span class="num-tag">// no visibility</span><h3>Spending feels invisible</h3><p>Money moves across food, apps, clothes and rides with nothing tying it together into a pattern you can actually see.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 3v3M12 18v3M3 12h3M18 12h3"/></svg></div><span class="num-tag">// no context</span><h3>No sense of "normal"</h3><p>Without a baseline, it's hard to know if $40 a week on food delivery is fine or a warning sign.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 15-6.7L21 8"/><path d="M21 3v5h-5"/><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-15 6.7L3 16"/><path d="M3 21v-5h5"/></svg></div><span class="num-tag">// no feedback loop</span><h3>Habits don't self-correct</h3><p>Behaviour only changes when someone gets a clear signal and a next step — not just a number.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="grid2">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">How the AI helps</span>
        <h2>SpendSense AI turns eight spending categories into one clear read on your behaviour.</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--ink-dim); margin-top:16px; font-size:15px;">You enter what you earn and what you spend. The engine classifies your behaviour as Low Spending Risk, Balanced, or High Spending Risk, then explains exactly which categories are driving that result — in your own numbers, not generic advice.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:0; overflow:hidden;">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="SpendSense AI results screen showing a risk badge and spending pulse waveform" style="display:block; width:100%; height:auto;">
        <p style="text-align:center; color:var(--ink-faint); font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; padding:14px;">a calm pulse = balanced spending</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <span class="eyebrow">Features</span>
    <h2>Everything you need to see the pattern and change it.</h2>
    <div class="grid3">
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3v18h18"/><path d="M7 15l4-5 3 3 5-7"/></svg></div><span class="num-tag">01</span><h3>Spending analysis</h3><p>Break down income and spending across 8 categories with an instant behaviour classification.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3a6 6 0 0 0-4 10.5c.5.5.8 1 .8 1.8V17h6.4v-1.7c0-.8.3-1.3.8-1.8A6 6 0 0 0 12 3z"/><path d="M9.5 20h5M10 17h4"/></svg></div><span class="num-tag">02</span><h3>AI insights &amp; recommendations</h3><p>Plain-language observations about where money is going, with specific next steps to try this week.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 11.5a8.4 8.4 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.4 8.4 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.4 8.4 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.4 8.4 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"/></svg></div><span class="num-tag">03</span><h3>Financial assistant chat</h3><p>Ask questions about your own results and get answers grounded in your actual numbers.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 17l6-6 4 4 8-8"/><path d="M14 7h7v7"/></svg></div><span class="num-tag">04</span><h3>Progress tracking</h3><p>Re-run your analysis over time and watch your risk category and savings rate move.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2l8 4v6c0 5-3.4 8.7-8 10-4.6-1.3-8-5-8-10V6l8-4z"/></svg></div><span class="num-tag">05</span><h3>Private by design</h3><p>Every account only ever sees its own data — nothing is shared across users.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20V10M12 10l-4 4M12 10l4 4"/><path d="M5 20h14"/><path d="M7 6a5 5 0 0 1 10 0"/></svg></div><span class="num-tag">06</span><h3>Built to grow</h3><p>The classifier is structured so a trained machine-learning model can be swapped in later.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="footer-cta">
    <h2>Ready to see your spending pulse?</h2>
    <button class="btn primary" onclick="go('signup')">Start Your Spending Analysis</button>
  </section>

  <div class="foot">SpendSense AI — a prototype financial behaviour assistant. Not a real bank or financial institution.</div>
</div>

<!-- ============ SIGNUP ============ -->
<div class="screen" id="screen-signup">
  <div class="auth-shell">
    <div class="auth-card">
      <h2>Create your account</h2>
      <p class="hint">Takes about a minute. Your data stays on your account only.</p>
